  {
    "post_title": "Attune: The Role of Focus in Authentic Leadership",
    "post_link": "https://www.billgeorge.org/articles/attune-the-role-of-focus-in-authentic-leadership1/",
    "post_date": "January 4, 2016",
    "post_content": [
      "<h2>About</h2><p>Reading glasses work well when you’re reading a book, but don’t try to drive across town wearing them. To do that, you need glasses that can change focus. The same is true with&nbsp;leadership. You need a different kind of focus to manage yourself, others, and the greater systems around you.</p><p><em><strong><a href=\"http://morethansound.net/shop/attune-the-role-of-focus-in-authentic-leadership/#.VoqZQpMrLoy\">Attune</a>: The Role of Focus in Authentic Leadership</strong></em>&nbsp;is a 40-minute streaming conversation between&nbsp;<a href=\"http://morethansound.net/authors/daniel-goleman/#.VnGYFcrNWCQ\">Daniel Goleman</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"http://morethansound.net/authors/bill-george/#.VnGX8MrNWCQ\">Bill George</a>&nbsp;about the three kinds of focus that are essential for enhancing your ability to give feedback,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/what-takes-become-socially-intelligent-leader-daniel-goleman?trk=mp-reader-card\">motivate people</a>, and&nbsp;<a href=\"http://morethansound.net/shop/thriving-on-change/#.VnGcFsrNWCQ\">respond to changing situations in your environment</a>.</p><em><strong><a href=\"http://morethansound.net/shop/attune-the-role-of-focus-in-authentic-leadership/#.VoqZQpMrLoy\">Attune</a>: The Role of Focus in Authentic Leadership</strong></em><strong><a href=\"http://morethansound.net/shop/attune-the-role-of-focus-in-authentic-leadership/#.VoqZQpMrLoy\">Attune</a>: The Role of Focus in Authentic Leadership</strong><a href=\"http://morethansound.net/shop/attune-the-role-of-focus-in-authentic-leadership/#.VoqZQpMrLoy\">Attune</a><a href=\"http://morethansound.net/authors/daniel-goleman/#.VnGYFcrNWCQ\">Daniel Goleman</a><a href=\"http://morethansound.net/authors/bill-george/#.VnGX8MrNWCQ\">Bill George</a><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/what-takes-become-socially-intelligent-leader-daniel-goleman?trk=mp-reader-card\">motivate people</a><a href=\"http://morethansound.net/shop/thriving-on-change/#.VnGcFsrNWCQ\">respond to changing situations in your environment</a><h2>Focus and Authentic Leadership</h2><p>Their discussion draws on examples from their own careers and those of business and world leaders, and highlights the benefits of developing each type of focus.</p><p><strong>Why inner focus?</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/how-self-awareness-impacts-your-work-daniel-goleman?trk=mp-reader-card\">Self-awareness</a>&nbsp;allows leaders to manage their inner world.</p><strong>Why inner focus?</strong><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/how-self-awareness-impacts-your-work-daniel-goleman?trk=mp-reader-card\">Self-awareness</a><p><strong>Why other focus?</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://morethansound.net/2015/05/21/how-compassion-can-transform-your-organization/#.VnGZvMrNWCQ\">Developing empathy</a>&nbsp;helps leaders build effective relationships and interactions.</p><strong>Why other focus?</strong><a href=\"http://morethansound.net/2015/05/21/how-compassion-can-transform-your-organization/#.VnGZvMrNWCQ\">Developing empathy</a><p><strong>Why outer focus?</strong>&nbsp;Awareness of larger systems helps leaders choose effective strategies.</p><strong>Why outer focus?</strong><p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/TBPRDOGtrUI\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/TBPRDOGtrUI\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe><p><strong style=\"font-size: 1.17em;\">Topics covered include:</strong></p><strong>Topics covered include:</strong><p>Learn the three types of empathy</p><p>Find your leadership blind spots</p><p>Giving and receiving feedback</p><p>Handling the heat in crucible moments</p><p>Understand the dangers of groupthink</p><p><a href=\"http://morethansound.net/shop/attune-the-role-of-focus-in-authentic-leadership/#.VoqZQpMrLoy\">Order Now!</a></p><a href=\"http://morethansound.net/shop/attune-the-role-of-focus-in-authentic-leadership/#.Voq