      "<p>In my recent interview with Sachin H. Jain for CardioSource WorldNews, I talk about the future of the medical device industry as well as the healthcare challenges facing the nation. To read the article, click <a href=\"https://www.billgeorge.org/files/media/media-files/Jain's%20Clinical%20Innovators%20-%20Bill%20George.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.&nbsp;</p><a href=\"https://www.billgeorge.org/files/media/media-files/Jain's%20Clinical%20Innovators%20-%20Bill%20George.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>"
