    "post_title": "Leading in Crisis: Lessons for Safety Leaders",
    "post_link": "https://www.billgeorge.org/articles/leading-in-crisis-lessons-for-safety-leaders/",
    "post_date": "March 1, 2010",
    "post_content": [
